<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/train">失忆症</a></p>
<p>以及与人合作过这些：<br />
<a href="/doomsday-tales">末世故事集</a> 合著者：<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agent-phage" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2950095); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2950095&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609230372" alt="Agent Phage" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2950095)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agent-phage" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2950095); return false;">Agent Phage</a></span>、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lyrics-linn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3935168); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3935168&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609230372" alt="Lyrics Linn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3935168)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lyrics-linn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3935168); return false;">Lyrics Linn</a></span>、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/colorlessl" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4396951); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4396951&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609230372" alt="ColorlessL" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4396951)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/colorlessl" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4396951); return false;">ColorlessL</a></span>、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/copperia" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5310502); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5310502&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609230372" alt="copperia" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5310502)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/copperia" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5310502); return false;">copperia</a></span>、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/df-thirteen" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4011450); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4011450&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609230372" alt="DF-thirteen" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4011450)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/df-thirteen" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4011450); return false;">DF-thirteen</a></span>、<span class="error-inline"><em>EveTerminus</em> does not match any existing user name</span>、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/star-lyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5096130); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5096130&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609230372" alt="Star Lyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5096130)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/star-lyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5096130); return false;">Star Lyn</a></span>、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/swanknight" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3342448); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3342448&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609230372" alt="SwanKnight" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3342448)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/swanknight" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3342448); return false;">SwanKnight</a></span>、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thomasx" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2789139); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2789139&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609230372" alt="ThomasX" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2789139)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thomasx" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2789139); return false;">ThomasX</a></span>、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/timeelapsed" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3662783); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3662783&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609230372" alt="TimeElapsed" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3662783)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/timeelapsed" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3662783); return false;">TimeElapsed</a></span>、<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wlft" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3975741); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3975741&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609230372" alt="wlft" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3975741)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wlft" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3975741); return false;">wlft</a></span><br />
<br />
简单来说是个对原则和底线态度明确，容不得差错和妥协的暴躁老姐，但与强势性格不符，除了勇气之外几乎没有任何过人之处。虽然在异常世界的战斗中留下一身伤痕，但暴躁老姐还是暴躁老姐，仍旧是充满正义感的强硬派。<br />
<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">派这种人去卧底还真是为难她了</span></p>
